  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Introduction:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a sandbox type role-playing game that includes simple simulation and strategy gameplay, a completely open game map, and no specific ending. Players can participate in events from various years in the game, and the theme combines characters from the Three Kingdoms and martial arts themes. This is a world that combines national power and folk life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Description of game features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main target event of the game is refreshed based on the date on the big map;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Numerous teammates and partners, including characters from the Three Kingdoms and martial arts, players can recruit them;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random challenger, if successful in battle, can receive item rewards;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various daily cultivation oriented gameplay in cities and strongholds; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automatic combat, with a clear and intuitive comparison of forces.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Introduction:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a sandbox type role-playing game that includes simple simulation and strategy gameplay, a completely open game map, and no specific ending. Players can participate in events from various years in the game, and the theme combines characters from the Three Kingdoms and martial arts themes. This is a world that combines national power and folk life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Description of game features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main target event of the game is refreshed based on the date on the big map;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Numerous teammates and partners, including characters from the Three Kingdoms and martial arts, players can recruit them;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random challenger, if successful in battle, can receive item rewards;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various daily cultivation oriented gameplay in cities and strongholds; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automatic combat, with a clear and intuitive comparison of forces.</p>",
